
### list tables

GET https://www.actito.be/ActitoWebServices/ws/v4/entity/{{entity}}/customTable
Authorization: Basic {{ws-token}}




### create webhook on offer assignment created
POST https://www.actito.be/ActitoWebServices/ws/v4/entity/{{entity}}/customTable/{{offerAssignmentsTable}}/webhookSubscription
Authorization: Basic {{ws-token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventType": "CREATE",
  "isActive": true,
  "onFields": [
  	"synchronized", "offerReference"
  ],
  "targetUrl": "{{function_root}}/enrichAssignment"
};

