### create webhook for updated profile with first store visit
POST https://www.actito.be/ActitoWebServices/ws/v4/entity/{{entity}}/table/{{profileTable}}/webhookSubscription
Authorization: Basic {{ws-token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventType": "UPDATE",
  "isActive": true,
  "onFields": [
  	"firstPurchaseDate"
  ],
